    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. RHI acceptance criterion (RHI < 1.0) is satisfied across all five CPB operating points. The assessment team has determined that the high-fidelity CFD parametric sweep, benchmarked against FDA pump study data, provides sufficient validation evidence for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The simulation-based validation is considered functionally equivalent to experimental validation given the maturity of the hemolysis modelling framework and the availability of published reference data. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1.",
